XDS110-ETP Evaluation Module
1 XDS110-ETP-EVM Overview
The XDS110-ETP mini debugger is a small and plug-and-play debug tool. This debugger keeps the main 
functions of TI launchpad debugger but is easier to use, and can be used for different target devices by one mini 
debugger board.
